&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18034413" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 31 Oct 2025 14:52:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So something in jolokia / vertx is reading the payload so its null&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18034455" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 31 Oct 2025 17:19:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Okay have a fix now&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
